fields.title: About the Developer
fields.content:
Kasem Al shadidi, is a Syrian nationality person who has a degree of Science in copmuter
and worked several years in IT-Support in Kuwait, and his dream was to be a developper
and to be a web designer, but his budget didn't allow him to take such a course in Full-stack software
developper as the course teaches so many techniques and programming languages, and cost
so much.

As he moved to Germany lately he found that the government supports such people who want to 
improve their career, he could finaly attend that powerfull course whom he dreamed.

With the "Agentur f‚Åør Arbeit" in Stuttgart he got a "Gutschein" (voucher) to attend acourse of  Full-stack software developper with Code Institute, he wants now to show what he learnt to the world
help him to improve the website and tell us what you suggest.
